    "uen": "201821822H",
    "description": "<p>Greenspade was founded in 2016 and is a startup comprising a small group of dynamic young people who love nature. Greenspade advocates green living in Singapore through promoting sustainable food waste initiatives, urban gardening practices and farming activities. We wish to bring nature a step closer to urbanised Singapore to make urban living sustainable, clean and green.<br>\n<br>\nGreenspade aims to provide an online platform that offers a slew of organic fertilisers, soil and gardening products. Greenspade also provides landscaping installation/maintenance services such as tree transplanting and irrigation. Greenspade is a one-stop, easy-access platform for all green living supporters and nature lovers. Through this, we hope to make gardening easy and a joy to everyone.<br>\n<br>\nIf you wish to find out more about our products and services, please get in touch with us at enquiry@greenspade.sg or call +65 8869-8827.</p>",
